    "english": "O Allah, on this day, (please) guide me to the virtuous deeds, and settle on this day all my needs and hopes. O He Who does not require explanation or wonderment! O He Who knows what is hidden in the chest of the peoples, (please) send blessings to Muhammad and his Household the immaculate."
